@startuml
title Figure 5.15: Send Completion Message Sequence Diagram

actor Administrator
participant "Dashboard Script\n(public/js/script.js)" as Script
participant "API Server\n(src/server.js)" as Api
participant "Orders Store\n(src/orders.js)" as Orders
participant "WhatsApp Client" as WhatsApp
actor Customer

Administrator -> Script : Click "Notify Ready"
Script -> Api : POST /api/notify/:id
Api -> Orders : getOrderById(id)
Orders --> Api : selected order
Api -> WhatsApp : sendMessage("Order is READY")
WhatsApp --> Customer : Ready / completion message
Api --> Script : success response
Script --> Administrator : Show notification sent

@enduml
